name: Paddle2ONNX v0.9.4
body:
# Experimental Feature 
- A new version of Paddle2ONNX is integrated in v0.9.4, which will make conversion faster and also optimize the converted onnx model. You can enable the new feature with flag `--enable_dev_version=True` https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle2ONNX/pull/669

# Bug Fix
- Fix bug of shape inference while exporting OCR model https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle2ONNX/pull/656
- Fix bug of `box_coder` under some onnx opset_version https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle2ONNX/pull/667
- Fix bug of  `unsqueeze` under some onnx opset_version https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle2ONNX/pull/652

# New Operators
- Support `mish`、`eye` and `one_hot_v2` https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle2ONNX/pull/663 https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle2ONNX/pull/655

name: Paddle2ONNX v0.9
body:
# New Feature
- Support define input shape dict. https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle2ONNX/pull/383


# New Operators and Functions
- `isfinite_v2`、`acos`、`asin`、`atan`、`ceil`、`cos`、`cosh`、`arg_min`、`elu` 、`hard_shrink` related pull request https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle2ONNX/pull/357
- `logical_not`、`logical_or`、`erf`、`isinf_v2`、`isnan`、`floor_mod`、`isnan_v2`、`less_than` 、`log2`、`logsumexp` related pull request https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle2ONNX/pull/358
-  `selu`、`logical_xor`、`log10`、`log1p`、`reduce_all`、`reduce_any`、`round`、`sin`、`rsqrt` 、`sign`、`logsigmoid` related pull request https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle2ONNX/pull/362
- `sinh`、`brelu`、`mv`、`dot`、`dist`、`softsign`、`log_softmax`、`argsort`、`index_select` 、`size`、`pad1d`、`hardtanh` related pull request https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle2ONNX/pull/363
- `conv3d `、`pool3d ` related pull request https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle2ONNX/pull/405
- Add onnx and onnxruntime version requirement prompts. https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle2ONNX/pull/335
- Add the op development guide for Paddle2ONNX.  https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle2ONNX/pull/368
- Add nms plugin for openvino. https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle2ONNX/pull/386

# Bug Fix
- `pool2d` operator, related pull request https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle2ONNX/pull/330
- `resize` operator, related pull request https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle2ONNX/pull/348
- `pad3` operator, related pull request https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle2ONNX/pull/349
- `concat` operator, related pull request https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle2ONNX/pull/377
- `argmax` operator, Fix bugs in argmax op when dtype is int32, related pull request https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle2ONNX/pull/393
- `padding ` operator, related pull request https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle2ONNX/pull/400
- `unsqueeze2 ` operator, related pull request https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle2ONNX/pull/405
- When exporting onnx, an error occurred when including a register_buffer. related pull request https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle2ONNX/pull/356

# Contributors
- Thanks to @AndPuQing for contributing 43 OPs in this release.
- Thanks to @SamDM for solving the problem of exporting models with register_buffer to ONNX in this release.
-  Thanks to @franva  for suggesting and fixing some small bugs for us in this release.

name: paddle2onnx 0.5
body:
This upgrade is mainly to support more official featured models, including PPYOLO, PPOCR, FasterRCNN, ERNIE and ViT. In addition, we have a more comprehensive coverage test for PaddleSeg and PaddleClas . For more detailed upgrade, refer to the following list:

- Support  PPYOLO, FasterRCNN, PPOCR, and ERNIE. Full support to convert PaddleClas models, including ViT (Vision Transformer). Please refer to docs/en/model_zoo.md
- Optimize the prompt of  OpMapper support status. 
- fix bug the incorrect input order of the model, such as yolov3.
- When pool is adative and ksize is [1,1], use gobal_pool to map adative_pool.
- Add a lot of English documents. 
- Add tutorial for converting dynamic computational graph to ONNX.

name: paddle2onnx 0.4
body:
- support paddle dygraph model convert to ONNX.
- add op_mapper register function
- support convert Paddle model(not combined)
- add [simple tutorial](https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/paddle2onnx/blob/develop/examples/tutorial.ipynb)
- add [op_list](https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/paddle2onnx/blob/develop/docs/en/op_list.md)

name: Paddle - ONNX Convertor
body:
Now support for convert Paddle Model to ONNX Opset 9, 10, 11. please use --onnx_opset to set opset_version of onnx you want to convert.

Add support for Paddle operators:
- swish 
- floor
- uniform_random
- abs
- instance_norm
- clip
- tanh
- log
- pad2d
- prelu

name: Paddle - ONNX Convertor
body:
Add more models  for PaddlePaddle Fluid model to ONNX model convertor. 

Supports the following models:

- SE_ResNet50_vd
- SqueezeNet1_0
- SE_ResNext50_32x4d
- Xception41
 - VGG16
 - InceptionV4
 - YoloV3

name: Paddle - ONNX Convertor
body:
First release of the PaddlePaddle Fluid model to ONNX model convertor. Also called a **frontend**.

Supports the following models:
- fit_a_line
- recognize_digits
- VGG16 & ResNet50
- MobileNet
- SE_ResNeXt
